@startuml
actor MerchantApp as "Merchant Application"
participant API as "Payment Provider API"
database DB as "PostgreSQL DB"
participant ExternalSystem as "External Payment System"

== Create Transaction ==

MerchantApp -> API: POST /api/v1/transactions (Basic Auth)
activate API

API -> API: Validate request
API -> API: Authenticate merchant

API -> DB: INSERT transaction (status=PENDING, merchant_id, amount, ...)
DB --> API: transaction ID

API -> MerchantApp: 201 Created (status=PENDING)

deactivate API

== Incoming Webhook ==

ExternalSystem -> API: POST /webhooks (eventType, entityId, payload)
activate API

API -> API: Validate webhook (signature, etc.)

API -> DB: INSERT INTO webhooks (event_type, entity_id, payload, notification_url)
note right: received_at = NOW()

API -> DB: UPDATE transaction SET status=SUCCESS/FAILED WHERE id = entity_id

API --> ExternalSystem: 200 OK

deactivate API

note right of API
  Аудит входящего вебхука:
  • сохраняется полный payload
  • фиксируется время получения
  • обновляется статус транзакции
end note

@enduml